description.en: HighLow Radio is a station of all hours. Running 24/7, you can be sure to get your licensed tunes, no matter the time. Sit down in the morning with a tea or coffee, tuning into our breakfast shows, or on your lunch break with food in hand, we're even online in your spare time, so no matter what you are doing, you can tune in.
description.ga_IE: Is stáisiún de gach uair an chloig é Radio Highilow.Ag rith 24/7, is féidir leat a bheith cinnte go bhfaighidh tú do chuid foinn cheadúnaithe, is cuma an t-am.Suigh síos ar maidin le tae nó caife, tiúnadh isteach inár seónna bricfeasta, nó ar do bhriseadh lóin le bia ar láimh, tá muid fiú ar líne i do chuid ama spártha, mar sin is cuma cad atá á dhéanamh agat, is féidir leat dul isteach ann.
